Sentencas: Sputtered coating of a low-Cr Fe-Co-Ni alloy with 0.36wt.% Si has been prepared on the same cast alloy via magnetron sputtering method.
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: The sputtered low-Cr alloy coating with columnar nanocrystalline structure is thermally oxidized in air at 800 degrees C corresponding to the cathode atmosphere of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: It is found that the oxidation resistance of the sputtered low-Cr alloy coating is significantly improved in comparison with the cast low-Cr alloy.
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: A double-layer oxide scale is thermally developed on the sputtered low-Cr alloy coating after oxidation for 12 weeks.
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: The outer layer is (Co,Fe)(3)O-4 spinel containing small amount of Ni and Cr.
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: The inner layer is a continuous Cr2O3 layer, followed by oxides of CrNbO4 and Nb2O5.
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: The surface scale formed on the sputtered coating after 12-week thermal exposure demonstrates an area specific resistance (ASR) of 31.97 m Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application

Sentencas: The sputtered low-Cr alloy nanocrystaline coating exhibits a promising perspective for intermediate temperature SOFC interconnects application.
Titulo: Sputtered nanocrystalline coating of a low-Cr alloy for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects application
